{"tid":1354924,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球迷向曼城球員講解香港情況並送上眼罩及黑口罩 工作人員瞬間收走","createTime":"2019-07-23T08:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T00:38:04.000Z","uid":9030,"like":117,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"db315d33cb3d032e02ed8236abc1e1e50e645a42","tid":1354924,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:36:35.000Z","msg":"大衛施華、辛真高和安祖連奴齊齊到銅鑼灣出席球衣品牌的活動，有球迷更特別送上護目鏡和黑口罩，希望三位球星可關注香港的逆權運動。<br />\n<br />\n在簽名會期間，球迷把護目鏡和黑色口罩送給大衛施華、辛真高和安祖連奴，希望他們可關注香港的逆權運動，惟工作人員瞬間收走相關物品。球迷透露臨時決定把護目鏡和黑色口罩送出：「在簽名時，我簡單向三人講解香港現時的情況，若他們發聲有很大影響力。」<br />\n<br />\n球迷續指三位球星亦有趨前聆聽自己的說話，並不時點頭，球迷說：「辛真高是烏克蘭人，其國家之前也經歷革命，他可能有興趣知道更多吧。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190723/large/1563864966_597b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190723%2Flarge%2F1563864966_597b.jpg&h=321fa1bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d310cbec7506c3d7b0318c1e0c50c1cb6be39b3","tid":1354924,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d94bdd64d94353a9ddd2c2aa3520affdd588305","tid":1354924,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98558924ea7993690437cf5667f1242988d2e73a","tid":1354924,"uid":9030,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190723/large/1563864966_0746.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190723%2Flarge%2F1563864966_0746.jpg&h=b560fcb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f72a3d56d99dfb44ebc4b9bb3e0fc731015d651","tid":1354924,"uid":9030,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:44:35.000Z","msg":"<